 and ends with a Headless Angel\\u2026These People are Demonic.\", \"from\": 6694, \"to\": 6932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6788, \"end\": 6791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9976102840514325, \"rank\": 0.0023089641884330805, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is Evil.\", \"from\": 6933, \"to\": 6946, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a kick in that face to the athletes who trained their whole lives to be here.\\\"\", \"from\": 6947, \"to\": 7030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another echoed: \\\"What the satanic bunch of bulls**t garbage is this?\", \"from\": 7032, \"to\": 7100, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why would anybody watch this garbage?\", \"from\": 7101, \"to\": 7138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Someone said she's supposed to be a bee over a hive of workers?\", \"from\": 7139, \"to\": 7202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Uhh then make it look like an actual (bee) @Paris2024 pure garbage, nothing else #Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 7203, \"to\": 7295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"2024 #Olympics Closing Ceremony: Beheaded white angel-performances remain just as shocking... as demonic as the opening ceremony,\\\" a third weighed in.\", \"from\": 7297, \"to\": 7448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While a fourth also wasn't impressed with the appearance of Nike: \\\"Soooo, an Angel w/it's head cut off symbolizes victory?\", \"from\": 7450, \"to\": 7572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7512, \"end\": 7516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.8945342989550912, \"rank\": 0.11764538143056145, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ok\\u2026 Seems rather demonic.\", \"from\": 7573, \"to\": 7598, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"#Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 7599, \"to\": 7610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Complaints continued to pour in from a fifth who hit out: \\\"The #Olympics opened up by mocking the Christian faith with disgraceful and disgusting recreation of the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 7612, \"to\": 7788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7712, \"end\": 7721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.997957341822211, \"rank\": 0.002046839170540625, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are doubling down and closing out with a dark and satanic closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 7789, \"to\": 7869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are supposed to be uplifting.\", \"from\": 7870, \"to\": 7912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not.\\\"\", \"from\": 7913, \"to\": 7926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And a sixth surmised: \\\"The #Olympics opened by mocking Christianity.\", \"from\": 7928, \"to\": 7996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7985, \"end\": 7997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999606590066714, \"rank\": 3.925937528282449e-05, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It ended with a satanic ritual.\\\"\", \"from\": 7997, \"to\": 8029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, there were some who jumped to the ceremony's defence, with one keen to point out: \\\"It's the Nike of Samothrace.\", \"from\": 8031, \"to\": 8151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's in the Louvre.\", \"from\": 8152, \"to\": 8171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's weird to show it like this.\", \"from\": 8172, \"to\": 8204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why not as the statue was originally fully formed?\", \"from\": 8205, \"to\": 8255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The wings are not big enough even so.\\\"\", \"from\": 8256, \"to\": 8294, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And others lauded the performance as a whole, including another who commented: \\\"This closing ceremony of the #OlympicGames has been everything that the opening ceremony wasn't.\", \"from\": 8296, \"to\": 8472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All told, a phenomenal Olympics that comfortably sits in the top 5 of all time #bbcolympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 8473, \"to\": 8566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(sic)  LATEST DEVELOPMENTS:  The Paris 2024 Olympic Games are over.Thank you \\ud83e\\udd79\\ud83d\\udcf8#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/2LaUDNnqjd  The criticism comes after Olympics organisers issued an apology for the offence caused by the Last Supper parody during the opening event last month.\", \"from\": 8567, \"to\": 8833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8608, \"end\": 8626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympic Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several religious groups openly criticised the display, including the Vatican which said: \\\"The Holy See was saddened by certain scenes at the opening ceremony of the Paris Olympic Games and cannot but join the voices raised in recent days to deplore the offense done to many Christians and believers of other religions.\", \"from\": 8835, \"to\": 9154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9114, \"end\": 9124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9708759795125309, \"rank\": 0.029640527377216643, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At a prestigious event where the whole world comes together to share common values, there should be no allusions ridiculing the religious convictions of many people.\", \"from\": 9156, \"to\": 9322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The freedom of expression, which is clearly not called into question here, is limited by respect for others,\\\" the Vatican added.\", \"from\": 9324, \"to\": 9453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps addressed the backlash soon after, telling the media: \\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 9455, \"to\": 9627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9459, \"end\": 9469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 5.017211098742366e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 9488, \"end\": 9496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[The opening ceremony] tried to celebrate community tolerance.\", \"from\": 9628, \"to\": 9690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 9692, \"to\": 9731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offence we are really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 9732, \"to\": 9786, \"entities\": []}]}"